### Summary of Ownership

| Object Type | Owner |
|-------------|-------|
| Core Roles | `SECURITYADMIN` |
| Databases | `{{ prefix }}_ADMIN` |
| Database Roles | `{{ prefix }}_RBAC` |
| Warehouses | `{{ prefix }}_ADMIN` |
| Warehouse Access Roles | `{{ prefix }}_RBAC` |
| Account Access Roles | `{{ prefix }}_RBAC` |
